    "feature_text_Vj93Ta": {
      "type": "feature-text",
      "settings": {
        "richtext": "<p>LEATHER GOODS PURCHASE AND COMMITMENT TO CRAFT<br/><br/>Last update: 15 April 2026<br/><br/>At PEGGY HARTANTO, we are deeply moved by the resonance our collections have found within our community. We acknowledge the frustration that arises when a desired piece is no longer available. Our commitment to excellence is an intentional journey, and we see it as our responsibility to maintain the quality and integrity of our production over the pursuit of scale.<br/><br/>We are constantly improving our production system and capacity. Due to the nature of the design, our leather goods production process involves precise cutting, delicate hand- painting and finishing, and complex construction; we are on an ongoing journey to optimizing our production pace without compromising the craftsmanship of the design.<br/><br/><br/><br/>ABOUT THE LEATHER GOODS PURCHASE<br/><br/>To ensure that our pieces reach our community in a transparent manner, we have implemented the following measures:<br/><br/>Acquisitions are limited to one (1) piece per SKU, per individual, per day.<br/><br/>To respect your time and provide an equitable experience for all, we have recently transitioned our boutique waiting lists to our Online Store. This ensures that every client, regardless of their location, has an equal opportunity to acquire our pieces as they become available.<br/><br/>We monitor our distribution methods daily and listen closely to the feedback from our community across all channels to ensure our system remains seamless.<br/><br/>We understand that waiting requires patience, and we sincerely thank you for valuing the hand-made nature of our product. We hope you will cherish your PEGGY HARTANTO pieces for a long time.<br/><br/><br/>ABOUT THE WAITLIST<br/><br/>If a leather good you were interested in is currently unavailable, we invite you to join the waitlist available on each SKU. Simply enter your email address to receive a notification as soon as the item is restocked.<br/><br/>If you have joined the waitlist at peggyhartanto.com but have not received an email notification:<br/><br/>Kindly check your spam or junk folder, as notifications may occasionally be filtered. Once a notification is sent and the item sells out, you will need to rejoin the waitlist to receive updates for the next restock.<br/><br/>If you have not received any notification, this indicates that the item has not yet been restocked.<br/><br/>Our waitlist system is designed for a one-time notification per restock cycle. If an item sells out before you have the opportunity to purchase, please re-register on the product page to be alerted for the next available batch.<br/><br/>For further inquiries regarding availability or  or giving input for making our purchase process better,  please contact us at <strong>lydia@peggyhartanto.com</strong>.<br/><br/></p>",
